verbose_text: Interestingly, results from triple-label ISH revealed that Hrh1 is expressed by both Nppb and Mrgpra3 neurons (93.3% +/- 0.8% of Nppb + cells and 73.4% +/- 2.3% of Mrgpra3 + cells; 1,644 and 1,185 neurons, respectively), as well as by an additional smaller population of cells (9.1% +/- 1.4% of Hrh1 + cells negative for Nppb and Mrgpra3; 286 neurons) (XREF_FIG and XREF_FIG).
